WEBVTT

00:00:29.375 --> 00:00:31.893
standing up against everything
this man stood for,

00:00:31.917 --> 00:00:35.476
and now, I was in his living room.

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:38.184
The day I met Craig Watts

00:00:38.208 --> 00:00:40.934
he had been raising chickens for 22 years

00:00:40.958 --> 00:00:42.726
for a company called Perdue,

00:00:42.750 --> 00:00:46.309
the fourth largest chicken company
in the entire country.

00:00:46.333 --> 00:00:47.601
And as a young man,

00:00:47.625 --> 00:00:51.434
he had yearned for this way
to stay on the land

00:00:51.458 --> 00:00:54.518
in one of the poorest
counties in the state.

00:00:54.542 --> 00:00:56.601
So when the chicken industry came to town,

00:00:56.625 --> 00:00:59.934
he thought, "This is a dream come true."

00:00:59.958 --> 00:01:02.768
He took a quarter
of a million dollar loan out,